    "### Exercise 3: Inverse Problem - Find α\n",
    "Given sparse temperature measurements, estimate the thermal diffusivity α."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    # Exercise 3: Inverse problem\nprint(\"Implement inverse heat equation!\")\nprint(\"Add alpha = nn.Parameter(torch.tensor(0.05))  # Learnable\")\nprint(\"Add data loss term from sparse observations\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
